===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|percynne||lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|frm}} {{term|persien||lang=frm}}, from {{etyl|it}} {{term|persiano|lang=it}}, from {{etyl|ML.}} {{term|Persianus|Persiānus|lang=la}}, blend of {{etyl|la}} {{term|Persia||lang=la}} and {{term|Asianus|Asiānus|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc}} {{term|sc=polytonic|Περσίς|tr=Persís|lang=grc}}, from {{etyl|peo}} {{term|sc=Xpeo|𐎱𐎠𐎼𐎿 |tr=Pārsa||Persia}} (compare modern Persian {{term|sc=fa-Arab|پارس|tr=Pārs|lang=la}}).

